{"data":[{"date":"16:10 06/07","title":"Walker ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 ph\u1ea3n \u1ee9ng c\u1ee7a Southgate sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng Colombia","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/19/walker-tiet-lo-phan-ung-cua-southgate-sau-tran-thang-colombia.PNG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Kyle Walker ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Gareth Southgate, ng\u00f4i sao \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Man City ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh v\u00ec vui qu\u00e1 \u0111\u00e3 qu\u00ean ch\u00fac m\u1eebng c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng Colombia.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kyle Walker ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 s\u1ed1c v\u1ec1 Gareth Southgate</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nAnh v\u00e0 Colombia \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u0103ng th\u1eb3ng \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/8 World Cup 2018. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u m\u00e0 h\u1ecd c\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u01b0ng l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a \u1edf nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng.\u00a0<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Kyle Walker ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Gareth Southgate h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Kyle Walker ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Gareth Southgate h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/19/walker-tiet-lo-phan-ung-cua-southgate-sau-tran-thang-colombia.PNG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Kyle Walker ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 Southgate qu\u00ean ch\u00fac m\u1eebng c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng Colombia</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nH\u00f2a 1-1 sau 120 ph\u00fat thi \u0111\u1ea5u bu\u1ed9c hai \u0111\u1ed9i ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e1 11m \u0111\u1ec3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u1ea5m v\u00e9 v\u00e0o t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft. Tr\u00ean ch\u1ea5m lu\u00e2n l\u01b0u may r\u1ee7i Anh v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc c\u1ee7a Jordan Pickford \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 4-3.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nKyle Walker ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Gareth Southgate, ng\u00f4i sao \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Man City ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh v\u00ec vui qu\u00e1 \u0111\u00e3 qu\u00ean ch\u00fac m\u1eebng c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng Colombia.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cSau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, \u00f4ng \u1ea5y \u0111i v\u00e0o ph\u00f2ng thay \u0111\u1ed5i v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng n\u00f3i g\u00ec c\u1ea3, \u00f4ng \u1ea5y ch\u1ec9 \u00f4m ch\u00fang t\u00f4i v\u1edbi v\u1ebb m\u1eb7t r\u1ea5t vui m\u1eebng. S\u00e1ng h\u00f4m sau \u00f4ng \u1ea5y n\u00f3i r\u1eb1ng v\u00ec vui m\u1eebng qu\u00e1 m\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 qu\u00ean ch\u00fac m\u1eebng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cNg\u00e0y h\u00f4m sau, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch t\u00edch c\u1ef1c, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c b\u1eaft tay v\u00e0o vi\u1ec7c chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Walker tin Anh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Anh \u0111\u00e3 l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1edbi v\u00f2ng t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft, \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd s\u1ebd l\u00e0 Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n. N\u1ebfu gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng B\u1eafc \u00c2u, Tam s\u01b0 s\u1ebd g\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ed9i th\u1eafng \u1edf c\u1eb7p Nga vs Croatia \u1edf b\u00e1n k\u1ebft.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Kyle Walker phan nan voi HLV\" title=\"Kyle Walker ph\u00e0n n\u00e0n v\u1edbi HLV\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/13/Arsene-Wenger-phat-bieu-ve-DT-Anh-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Kyle Walker tin Anh \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTh\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n, Nga v\u00e0 Croatia \u0111\u1ec1u b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 th\u1ea5p h\u01a1n Anh, b\u1edfi v\u1eady con \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng v\u00e0o chung k\u1ebft \u0111ang r\u1ed9ng m\u1edf tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eb7t Tam s\u01b0. Walker tin Anh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111ang \u0111\u1ea1t phong \u0111\u1ed9 t\u1ed1t \u1edf World Cup 2018, to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111ang quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m tr\u01b0\u1edbc Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd ch\u01a1i c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng trong t\u1eebng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, Anh \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ec3 v\u00e0o tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft v\u00e0 l\u00ean ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/hlv-southgate-bay-gio-hoac-khong-bao-gio-cho-dt-anh-421-190481.html\" target=\"_blank\">Gareth Southgate n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 \u0110T Anh</span>, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y 47 tu\u1ed5i c\u0169ng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ec3 Tam s\u01b0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch, h\u1ecd s\u1ebd c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ee5 s\u1ef1 tin t\u01b0\u1edfng n\u01a1i NHM.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"968","checkdouble":"190515"},{"date":"16:27 06/07","title":"Th\u1ef1c h\u01b0 v\u1ee5 Arsenal chi 27 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua Cristian Pavon","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/6/pavon.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Th\u00f4ng tin Arsenal mua Cristian Pavon th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 27 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00fang s\u1ef1 th\u1ef1c, \u0111\u00edch th\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Arsenal \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 quan t\u00e2m Pavon</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Cristian Pavon l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Boca Juniors. Ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1996 \u0111\u00e3 ghi t\u1edbi 6 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00e0 cung c\u1ea5p 11 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o sau 26 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u cao nh\u1ea5t b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Argentina.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Th\u1ef1c h\u01b0 v\u1ee5 Arsenal mua Cristian Pavon h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Th\u1ef1c h\u01b0 v\u1ee5 Arsenal mua Cristian Pavon h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/2/Thuc-hu-vu-Arsenal-mua-Cristian-Pavon-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Arsenal quan t\u00e2m Pavon</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 22 tu\u1ed5i r\u1ea5t \u0111a n\u0103ng, anh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u1edf c\u1ea3 hai c\u00e1nh, ch\u01a1i \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed h\u1ed9 c\u00f4ng ho\u1eb7c trung phong c\u1eafm. \u0110i\u1ec3m m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a Pavon l\u00e0 t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9, k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng qua ng\u01b0\u1eddi v\u00e0 nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng l\u1eadt b\u00f3ng ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c t\u1eeb hai bi\u00ean.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTheo Mirror, HLV Unai Emery c\u1ee7a Arsenal \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina v\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a anh v\u1ec1 s\u00e2n Emirates.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTh\u1eadm ch\u00ed t\u1edd b\u00e1o c\u1ee7a n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh c\u00f2n kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 c\u1eed ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n, h\u1ecd \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Pavon v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 27 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Pavon</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u00f4ng tin Arsenal mua Cristian Pavon th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 27 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00fang s\u1ef1 th\u1ef1c, \u0111\u00edch th\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n Fernando Hidalgo c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Th\u1ef1c h\u01b0 v\u1ee5 Arsenal mua Cristian Pavon h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"Th\u1ef1c h\u01b0 v\u1ee5 Arsenal mua Cristian Pavon h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/6/pavon.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn Arsenal ch\u01b0a h\u1ecfi mua Pavon</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cKh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 g\u00ec ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c t\u1eeb Arsenal. T\u00f4i ch\u01b0a h\u1ec1 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u00f4ng tin v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c Arsenal mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 th\u00e2n ch\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng n\u00e0o \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u00f4ng qua c\u1ea3, \u0111\u00f3 ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 th\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e1o ch\u00ed \u0111\u1ed3n th\u1ed5i\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nCh\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Boca, Daniel Angelici tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 r\u1eb1ng Pavon s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng ra \u0111i v\u1edbi b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 gi\u00e1 n\u00e0o, \u00f4ng n\u00e0y mu\u1ed1n gi\u1eef ng\u00f4i sao 22 tu\u1ed5i \u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Argentina.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201c Hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ch\u01b0a nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb n\u00e0o, d\u00f9 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c hay kh\u00f4ng ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i bi\u1ebft r\u00f5 t\u1ea7m quan tr\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a Pavon, vi\u1ec7c gia\u00a0h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng cho th\u1ea5y ch\u00fang t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n gi\u1eef c\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u1edf l\u1ea1i m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch l\u00e2u d\u00e0i\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cBoca \u01b0u ti\u00ean gi\u1eef Pavon \u1edf l\u1ea1i, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd l\u00e0m m\u1ecdi c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n c\u1eadu \u1ea5y. Pavon l\u00e0 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a Boca, t\u00f4i v\u00e0 BL\u0110 \u0111\u1ec1u bi\u1ebft r\u00f5 \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"967","checkdouble":"190516"},{"date":"16:30 06/07","title":"Nh\u1eefng d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n h\u1ee3p th\u1eddi cho tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u s\u1edbm Ph\u00e1p vs Uruguay","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/6/truc-tiep-uruguay-vs-phap.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp Uruguay vs Ph\u00e1p: C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Ph\u00e1p vs Uruguay t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 l\u00fac 21h00 t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 6/7.</h2><h2>Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp Uruguay vs Ph\u00e1p: C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Ph\u00e1p vs Uruguay t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 l\u00fac 21h00 t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 6/7.</h2>\r\nKh\u00f4ng xem \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c, vui l\u00f2ng click v\u00e0o \u0111\u00e2y <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/truc-tiep-world-cup-2018/tran-dau/truc-tiep-uruguay-vs-phap-463-190521.html\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(128, 0, 0);\"><u><strong>TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP URUGUAY VS PH\u00c1P</strong></u></span></span><br>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"966","checkdouble":"190517"},{"date":"17:00 06/07","title":"Klopp: Karius b\u1ecb sang ch\u1ea5n t\u00e2m l\u00fd nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/29/klopp-phat-bieu-ve-karius-cua-liverpool.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Klopp ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Karius, h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 t\u1ea1i Liverpool. Nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb ch\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u00e2m l\u00fd nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng sau tr\u1eadn thua Real Madrid.</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nKarius v\u00e0 h\u1ec7 l\u1ee5y t\u1eeb tr\u1eadn thua Real</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nLoris Karius \u0111\u00e3 m\u1eafc ph\u1ea3i 2 sai l\u1ea7m l\u1edbn khi\u1ebfn Liverpool h\u1ee9ng ch\u1ecbu tr\u1eadn thua 1-3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Real Madrid t\u1ea1i chung k\u1ebft Champions League m\u00f9a 2017/18. \u0110\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, anh n\u00e9m b\u00f3ng th\u1eb3ng v\u00e0o ch\u00e2n Karim Benzema khi\u1ebfn The Kop b\u1ecb m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc. V\u1ec1 cu\u1ed1i tr\u1eadn, Karius l\u1ea1i b\u1eaft b\u00f3ng h\u1ecfng khi\u1ebfn h\u1ecd thua b\u00e0n th\u1ee9 3.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nHi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, HLV Jurgen Klopp c\u00f9ng m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Liverpool kh\u00f4ng d\u1ef1 World Cup 2018 \u0111\u00e3 quay tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i trung t\u00e2m Melwood \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi. Tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi ph\u00f3ng vi\u00ean, Klopp chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 h\u1eadu qu\u1ea3 c\u1ee7a th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Real c\u00f9ng pha va ch\u1ea1m v\u00e0o Sergio Ramos v\u1edbi Karius.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Klopp ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Karius, h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 t\u1ea1i Liverpool h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Klopp ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Karius, h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 t\u1ea1i Liverpool h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/29/klopp-phat-bieu-ve-karius-cua-liverpool.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Klopp ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Karius v\u00e0 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh anh b\u1ecb \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng t\u00e2m l\u00fd</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cSau tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft, \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t b\u00e1c s\u0129 g\u1ecdi cho t\u00f4i v\u00e0 n\u00f3i: Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb ch\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ed9ng\u201d, Klopp ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Karius. \u201cT\u00f4i ngh\u0129 \u0111\u00e3 qu\u00e1 mu\u1ed9n, b\u1ea1n kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ki\u1ec3m tra \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3. Nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i bi\u1ebft ch\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ed9ng kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ebfn v\u00e0 \u0111i trong m\u1ed9t ng\u00e0y. N\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n r\u01a1i v\u00e0o t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng \u0111\u00f3, b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd hi\u1ec3u.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201c5 ng\u00e0y sau, Karius v\u1eabn c\u00f2n nguy\u00ean ch\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ed9ng. N\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n h\u1ecfi, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1ebd n\u00f3i kh\u00f4ng ngh\u0129 v\u1ec1 n\u00f3 v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng d\u00f9ng n\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 b\u00e0o ch\u1eefa. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng n\u00f3 nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t c\u00e1i c\u1edb, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng n\u00f3 nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t l\u1eddi gi\u1ea3i th\u00edch. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y b\u1ecb \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng b\u1edfi pha va ch\u1ea1m v\u1edbi Ramos, 100%.\u201d<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>B\u1ecf l\u1ea1i qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9 \u0111\u1eb1ng sau</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nKlopp cho bi\u1ebft Karius v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Real sau l\u01b0ng b\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5p s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m t\u1eeb truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng. Chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u00f3 kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u m\u1edbi \u1edf m\u00f9a 2018/19. \u201cN\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n m\u1eafc sai l\u1ea7m trong tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft Champions League, b\u1ea1n kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thay \u0111\u1ed5i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u00f3 ngay c\u1ea3 khi b\u1ea1n mu\u1ed1n, t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ec1u mu\u1ed1n\u201d, Klopp n\u00f3i th\u00eam.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cL\u00fd gi\u1ea3i t\u1ea1i sao m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 x\u1ea3y ra l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u lu\u00f4n r\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng. V\u00ec v\u1eady, \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi t\u00f4i, m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1ng lo ng\u1ea1i. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng ngh\u0129 v\u1ec1 \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 n\u1eefa v\u00e0 h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi m\u1ed9t kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u m\u1edbi.\u201d<br>\r\n<strong><br>\r\nXem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 Liverpool tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/thuc-hu-vu-klopp-muon-liverpool-mua-xherdan-shaqiri-172-190490.html\">Th\u1ef1c h\u01b0 v\u1ee5 Klopp mu\u1ed1n Liverpool mua Xherdan Shaqiri</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/fabinho-khang-dinh-chua-tung-tien-gan-mu-172-190409.html\">Fabinho ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 s\u1ef1 th\u1eadt v\u1ec1 v\u1ee5 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u1ee5t v\u1edbi MU</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/tan-binh-liverpool-len-tieng-choc-tuc-man-utd-172-190403.html\">T\u00e2n binh Liverpool l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng ch\u1ecdc t\u1ee9c Man Utd</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/shaqiri-muon-o-lai-premier-league-172-190387.html\">Sao sa c\u01a1 \u0111\u00e1nh ti\u1ebfng c\u1ea7u c\u1ee9u Liverpool</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/hlv-klopp-phat-bieu-ve-viec-salah-gia-han-hop-dong-voi-liverpool-172-190179.html\">Salah gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u00e0 th\u00f4ng \u0111i\u1ec7p t\u1eeb Liverpool</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/salah-chinh-thuc-ky-hop-dong-dai-han-voi-liverpool-172-190174.html\">Salah k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng d\u00e0i h\u1ea1n v\u1edbi Liverpool, t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i Real</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"965","checkdouble":"190518"},{"date":"17:37 06/07","title":"Thua x\u1ea5u x\u00ed, \u0110T Colombia v\u1eabn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3n nh\u01b0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng khi v\u1ec1 n\u01b0\u1edbc","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/6/thua-xau-xi-dt-colombia-van-duoc-chao-don-nhu-nguoi-hung-khi-ve-nuoc.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, Falcao v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 Bogota sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018. Tuy nhi\u00ean, \u0110T Colombia \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3n nhi\u1ec7t t\u00ecnh nh\u01b0 nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng.\r\n</h2><h2>Colombia ho\u00e0nh tr\u00e1ng tr\u1edf v\u1ec1<br />\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau khi xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110T Anh \u1edf nh\u1eefng gi\u00e2y ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng, Colombia kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c l\u00e0m n\u00ean \u0111i\u1ec1u b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 g\u1ee5c ng\u00e3 trong lo\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ea5u s\u00fang 11m. \u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 khi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n Nam M\u1ef9 \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i gi\u1ea5c m\u01a1 World Cup, v\u00e0 l\u00ean m\u00e1y bay v\u1ec1 n\u01b0\u1edbc ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u m\u00e0 th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Jose Pekerman \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7y ti\u1ec3u x\u1ea3o v\u00e0 b\u1ea1o l\u1ef1c, nh\u1eadn t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng 6 chi\u1ebfc th\u1ebb v\u00e0ng, nh\u01b0ng v\u1eabn kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng. Nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 nh\u01b0 Mateus Uribe, Carlos Bacca (tr\u01b0\u1ee3t ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n) v\u00e0 Carlos Sanchez (g\u00e2y ra 2 qu\u1ea3 pen tr\u01b0\u1edbc Nh\u1eadt v\u00e0 Anh), th\u1eadm ch\u00ed \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb \u0111e d\u1ecda m\u1ea1ng s\u1ed1ng n\u1ebfu tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 n\u01b0\u1edbc.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110T Colombia \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3n nhi\u1ec7t t\u00ecnh t\u1ea1i th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4 Bogata\" title=\"\u0110T Colombia \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3n\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/6/thua-xau-xi-dt-colombia-van-duoc-chao-don-nhu-nguoi-hung-khi-ve-nuoc.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>\u0110T Colombia \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3n nhi\u1ec7t t\u00ecnh t\u1ea1i th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4 Bogata</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\nNh\u01b0ng r\u1ed3i, r\u1ea5t may \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh n\u00e0o \u0111\u00e1ng ti\u1ebfc n\u00e0o x\u1ea3y ra. Tr\u00e1i l\u1ea1i, ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00e2n Colombia ch\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3n \u0110T qu\u1ed1c gia tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 nh\u01b0 nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u r\u1ea5t \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng, n\u1ebfu bi\u1ebft r\u1eb1ng Colombia l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng s\u1edf h\u1eefu s\u1ed1 C\u0110V sang Nga c\u1ed5 v\u0169 nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1ea5t, kho\u1ea3ng 50 ngh\u00ecn ng\u01b0\u1eddi.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Bogata, th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4 Colombia &ndash; Falcao v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 ch\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3n ngo\u00e0i mong \u0111\u1ee3i. H\u00e0ng ng\u00e0n ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 \u0111\u00e3 x\u1ebfp h\u00e0ng tr\u00ean c\u00e1c \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ph\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ec3 \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9, v\u00e0 ch\u0103ng nh\u1eefng t\u1ea5m bi\u1ec3u ng\u1eef cho c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7. \u0110\u00e1p l\u1ea1i, HLV Pekerman v\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Falcao \u0111\u00e3 v\u1eaby tay ch\u00e0o c\u00e1c C\u0110V nhi\u1ec7t t\u00ecnh nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi n\u00e0y.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed, qu\u00e2n \u0111\u1ed9i Colombia c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ee9ng ngo\u00e0i cu\u1ed9c vui, khi x\u1ebfp h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u00e0o m\u1eebng c\u00e1c ng\u00f4i sao tr\u1edf v\u1ec1. R\u00f5 r\u00e0ng cho d\u00f9 kh\u00f4ng g\u00e2y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u1ea1nh h\u01b0 k\u1ef3 World Cup 4 n\u0103m tr\u01b0\u1edbc (l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft), nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Nam M\u1ef9 v\u1eabn l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng trong m\u1eaft ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00e2n c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110T Colombia \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3n nhi\u1ec7t t\u00ecnh, \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp th\u00eam \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u1ef1c \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1ecd chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u trong nh\u1eefng gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1edbn ti\u1ebfp theo.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/gan-200-nghin-nguoi-ky-don-doi-anh-va-colombia-da-lai-421-190506.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/6/gan-200-nghin-nguoi-ky-don-doi-anh-va-colombia-da-lai.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/gan-200-nghin-nguoi-ky-don-doi-anh-va-colombia-da-lai-421-190506.html\">G\u1ea7n 200 ngh\u00ecn ng\u01b0\u1eddi k\u00fd \u0111\u01a1n \u0111\u00f2i Anh v\u00e0 Colombia \u0111\u00e1 l\u1ea1i</span><br />\r\nB\u1ee9c th\u01b0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kh\u1edfi x\u01b0\u1edbng b\u1edfi nh\u00f3m C\u0110V Colombia, nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi cho r\u1eb1ng tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh sai \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00f2ng 1/8.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/colombia-vs-anh-01-tieu-xao-sai-lam-va-nhung-dac-trung-lam-nen-tran-cau-sieu-kich-tinh-421-190343.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/4/colombia-vs-anh-01-tieu-xao-sai-lam-va-nhung-dac-trung-lam-nen-tran-cau-sieu-kich-tinh.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/colombia-vs-anh-01-tieu-xao-sai-lam-va-nhung-dac-trung-lam-nen-tran-cau-sieu-kich-tinh-421-190343.html\">D\u01b0 \u00e2m Colombia 1-1 (pen 3-4) Anh: Ti\u1ec3u x\u1ea3o, sai l\u1ea7m v\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1eb7c tr\u01b0ng l\u00e0m n\u00ean tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u si\u00eau k\u1ecbch t\u00ednh</span><br />\r\n\u0110\u00eam qua, tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u h\u1ea1 m\u00e0n v\u00f2ng 1/8 World Cup 2018 \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i, v\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng d\u00e0nh cho th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Gareth Southgate. D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng d\u01b0 \u00e2m tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Colombia vs...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"964","checkdouble":"190520"},{"date":"17:03 06/07","title":"TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP Uruguay vs Ph\u00e1p 21h00 ng\u00e0y 6/7 (World Cup 2018)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/6/truc-tiep-uruguay-vs-phap.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp Uruguay vs Ph\u00e1p: C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Ph\u00e1p vs Uruguay t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 l\u00fac 21h00 t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 6/7.</h2><h2>Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp Uruguay vs Ph\u00e1p: C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Ph\u00e1p vs Uruguay t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 l\u00fac 21h00 t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 6/7.</h2>\r\nKh\u00f4ng xem \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c, vui l\u00f2ng click v\u00e0o \u0111\u00e2y <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/truc-tiep-world-cup-2018/tran-dau/truc-tiep-uruguay-vs-phap-463-190521.html\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(128, 0, 0);\"><u><strong>TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP URUGUAY VS PH\u00c1P</strong></u></span></span><br>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"963","checkdouble":"190521"},{"date":"17:26 06/07","title":"\u0110T Anh thi\u1ec7t qu\u00e2n tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup 2018","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/6/vardy-dinh-chan-thuong-nhieu-kha-nang-lo-tu-ket.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Jamie Vardy d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng h\u00e1ng v\u00e0 v\u1eafng m\u1eb7t \u1edf bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a \u0110T Anh. Nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o 31 tu\u1ed5i s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng k\u1ecbp b\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ec3 d\u1ef1 tr\u1eadn t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 v\u1edbi Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Vardy ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng h\u00e1ng</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u1ede tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng Colombia v\u00f2ng 1/8 World Cup 2018, Jamie Vardy \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Gareth Southgate tung v\u00e0o s\u00e2n trong nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i c\u1ee7a th\u1eddi gian thi \u0111\u1ea5u ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c. Sau \u0111\u00f3 5 ph\u00fat, t\u1ee9c ph\u00fat b\u00f9 gi\u1edd th\u1ee9 3, \u0110T Anh b\u1ecb g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a 1-1 v\u00e0 ph\u1ea3i b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o hi\u1ec7p ph\u1ee5.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong th\u1eddi gian n\u00e0y, Vardy d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng h\u00e1ng v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 tham gia lo\u1ea1t lu\u00e2n l\u01b0u 11m sau \u0111\u00f3. Ngay c\u1ea3 khi \u0110T Anh gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 4-3 \u1edf lo\u1ea1t \u201c\u0111\u1ea5u s\u00fang\u201d, ch\u00e2n s\u00fat c\u1ee7a Leicester City c\u0169ng t\u1ecf ra g\u01b0\u1ee3ng g\u1ea1o khi ch\u1ea1y ra \u0103n m\u1eebng c\u00f9ng c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Vardy d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng h\u00e1ng v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng d\u1ef1 bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t \u0110T Anh h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Vardy d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng h\u00e1ng v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng d\u1ef1 bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t \u0110T Anh h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/6/vardy-dinh-chan-thuong-nhieu-kha-nang-lo-tu-ket.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Vardy d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng h\u00e1ng v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng d\u1ef1 bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Kh\u00f4ng d\u1ef1 bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110T Anh \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m qua \u0111\u1ec3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup 2018 v\u1edbi Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n. \u0110\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Th\u1ee5y S\u0129 1-0 d\u1ef1a tr\u00ean s\u1ef1 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn c\u1ee7a h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 c\u00f9ng nh\u1eefng pha ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng l\u1ee3i h\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ec3 ghi t\u00ean v\u00e0o t\u1ed1p 8 \u0111\u1ed9i xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u00e0o l\u00fac 21h t\u1ed1i mai (7/7), Anh s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Samara Arena. D\u00f9 v\u1eady, Vardy v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n b\u00ecnh th\u01b0\u1eddng c\u00f9ng to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i. Nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ch\u00e2n s\u00fat sinh n\u0103m 1987 s\u1ebd v\u1eafng m\u1eb7t \u1edf m\u00e0n so t\u00e0i v\u1edbi Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n, n\u01a1i Tam s\u01b0 c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o chung k\u1ebft v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i th\u1eafng trong c\u1eb7p Nga vs Croatia.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNgo\u00e0i Vardy, HLV Southgate kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00f3n th\u00eam tin k\u00e9m vui n\u00e0o t\u1eeb c\u00e1c tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t. Nh\u1eefng Ashley Young, Kyle Walker, Dele Alli v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng Harry Kane \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e3 l\u1ea5y l\u1ea1i th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t sau m\u00e0n so t\u00e0i n\u00f3ng b\u1ecfng v\u1edbi Colombia. Fabian Delph c\u0169ng tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i t\u1eadp trung sau khi v\u1ec1 n\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3n s\u1ef1 ra \u0111\u1eddi c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi con th\u1ee9 3.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 \u0110T Anh tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/sao-tuyen-anh-colombia-la-doi-thu-ban-nhat-toi-tung-biet-421-190479.html\">Sao tuy\u1ec3n Anh: Colombia l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 b\u1ea9n nh\u1ea5t t\u00f4i t\u1eebng bi\u1ebft</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/vi-ly-do-nay-tuyen-anh-chap-nhan-mang-tieng-kich-si-421-190462.html\">V\u00ec l\u00fd do n\u00e0y, tuy\u1ec3n Anh ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn mang ti\u1ebfng \u201ck\u1ecbch s\u0129\u201d</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/tin-nong-world-cup-2018/ibrahimovic-thuy-dien-se-lam-cho-dt-anh-phai-cam-nin-469-190454.html\">Ibrahimovic: Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n s\u1ebd l\u00e0m cho \u0110T Anh ph\u1ea3i c\u00e2m n\u00edn</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/dt-anh-vo-dich-world-cup-tai-sao-khong-421-190437.html\">\u0110T Anh v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup: T\u1ea1i sao kh\u00f4ng?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/dt-anh-giong-voi-tay-ban-nha-nam-2010-421-190424.html\">\u0110T Anh gi\u1ed1ng v\u1edbi T\u00e2y Ban Nha n\u0103m 2010</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"962","checkdouble":"190522"},{"date":"17:55 06/07","title":"Conte nh\u1eafn g\u1eedi Chelsea: \"T\u00f4i v\u1eabn c\u00f2n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ea5y nh\u00e9!\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/13/conte-nhan-gui-chelsea-toi-van-co-hop-dong-day-nhe.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>D\u00f9 coi nh\u01b0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1eeba t\u1ea1i The Blues l\u00fac n\u00e0y, nh\u01b0ng HLV Antonio Conte t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i r\u1eddi Chelsea khi cho r\u1eb1ng, \u00f4ng v\u1eabn c\u00f2n cam k\u1ebft t\u1ea1i CLB.\r\n</h2><h2>Conte v\u1eabn \u0111\u00f2i quy\u1ec1n h\u00e0nh \u1edf Chelsea<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u00f9a h\u00e8 t\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London ch\u01b0a bao gi\u1edd r\u1eafc r\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ebfn th\u1ebf. Trong l\u00fac c\u00e1c k\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ecbch t\u1ea5t b\u1eadt v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi, Chelsea v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chi\u1ebfc gh\u1ebf HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng. H\u1ecd th\u1eadm ch\u00ed kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft ai s\u1ebd d\u1eabn d\u1eaft \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi, v\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 l\u00fd do Chelsea v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9ng th\u00e1i g\u00ec tr\u00ean th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, The Blues \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m Maurizio Sarri, nh\u01b0ng h\u1ecd v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft v\u1ee5 Antonio Conte. Theo \u0111\u00f3, Conte mu\u1ed1n nh\u1eadn to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n b\u1ed3i th\u01b0\u1eddng 9 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho 1 n\u0103m h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i, trong khi \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Stamford Bridge v\u1eabn \u0111ang d\u00f9ng d\u1eb1ng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong kho\u1ea3ng th\u1eddi gian n\u00e0y, chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia 48 tu\u1ed5i v\u1eabn c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t t\u1ea1i SV\u0110 \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c. Theo th\u00f4ng tin m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c The Times \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i, Conte \u0111\u00e3 m\u00e2u thu\u1eabn v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng nh\u00e2n vi\u00ean k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt \u1edf \u0111\u00e2y. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, khi m\u1ed9t nh\u00e2n vi\u00ean c\u1ee7a Chelsea \u0111\u1ecbnh g\u1eedi email cho c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 kh\u00f4ng tham d\u1ef1 World Cup, r\u1eb1ng h\u1ecd c\u1ea7n tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 CLB v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec3 ki\u1ec3m tra \u00fd t\u1ebf - Conte \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i kh\u00f4ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Conte t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i r\u1eddi Chelsea, quy\u1ebft \u0111\u00f2i b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ti\u1ec1n gi\u1ea3i ph\u00f3ng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng\" title=\"Chelsea Conte ava\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/14/du-am-newcastle-vs-chelsea-phia-truoc-la-dia-nguc.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Conte t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i r\u1eddi Chelsea, quy\u1ebft \u0111\u00f2i b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ti\u1ec1n gi\u1ea3i ph\u00f3ng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nChi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi b\u1eb1ng tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1, \u00f4ng v\u1eabn c\u00f2n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng t\u1ea1i Chelsea v\u00e0 ch\u1ecbu tr\u00e1ch nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ec1 l\u1ecbch tr\u00ecnh c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7. \u00d4ng y\u00eau c\u1ea7u h\u1ecd c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n, v\u00e0 th\u1ee9 Hai tu\u1ea7n sau m\u1edbi ph\u1ea3i h\u1ed9i qu\u00e2n.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">R\u1eafc r\u1ed1i trong cu\u1ed9c chi\u1ebfn th\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ea7ng, d\u1ec5 hi\u1ec3u v\u00ec sao Chelsea l\u00fac n\u00e0y v\u1eabn r\u1ed1i nh\u01b0 t\u01a1 v\u00f2, v\u00e0 ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi &ndash; ch\u1ec9 5 tu\u1ea7n tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi Premier League b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u. Tuy nhi\u00ean, CLB th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4 n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a mu\u1ed1n b\u1ed3i th\u01b0\u1eddng ti\u1ec1n cho Antonio Conte, khi h\u1ecd c\u00f2n ph\u1ea3i g\u00e1nh th\u00eam chi ph\u00ed cho \u0111\u1ed9i ng\u0169 tr\u1ee3 l\u00fd bao g\u1ed3m c\u1ea3 9 ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1ee7a HLV n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Conte t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i r\u1eddi Chelsea, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed \u00f4ng c\u00f2n x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ebd ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i 1 n\u0103m \u0111\u1ec3 b\u00f2n r\u00fat t\u1ed1i \u0111a t\u1eeb CLB. Theo cam k\u1ebft, n\u1ebfu HLV Italia kh\u00f4ng t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi trong v\u00f2ng 1 n\u0103m, Chelsea s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i ho\u00e0n tr\u1ea3 l\u1ea1i to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n 1 n\u0103m h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng. D\u00f9 sao, \u0111\u00f3 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 \u0111\u00f2i h\u1ecfi \u0111\u00fang \u0111\u1eafn, b\u1edfi The Blues \u0111\u00e3 qu\u00e1 thi\u1ebfu t\u00f4n tr\u1ecdng thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-se-phai-mua-ca-doi-hinh-neu-de-willian-va-hazard-ra-di-172-190498.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/6/chelsea-se-phai-mua-ca-doi-hinh-neu-de-willian-va-hazard-ra-di.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-se-phai-mua-ca-doi-hinh-neu-de-willian-va-hazard-ra-di-172-190498.html\">Chelsea s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i tr\u1ea3 gi\u00e1 \u0111\u1eaft n\u1ebfu \u0111\u1ec3 Willian v\u00e0 Hazard ra \u0111i</span><br>\r\nC\u1ef1u h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Wayne Bridge cho r\u1eb1ng Chelsea s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i mua l\u1ea1i c\u1ea3 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh n\u1ebfu \u0111\u1ec3 hai ng\u00f4i sao t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng Willian v\u00e0 Hazard ra \u0111i h\u00e8 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-vuot-mat-con-moi-vi-real-madrid-172-190411.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/3/chelsea-vuot-mat-con-moi-vi-real-madrid.PNG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-vuot-mat-con-moi-vi-real-madrid-172-190411.html\">Chelsea vu\u1ed9t m\u1ea5t con m\u1ed3i v\u00ec... Real Madrid</span><br>\r\nTheo th\u00f4ng tin t\u1eeb ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Argentina &ndash; Gonzalo Higuain t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i Chelsea v\u00ec m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9ng th\u00e1i b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd tr\u00ean th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"961","checkdouble":"190524"},{"date":"17:30 06/07","title":"Tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00f2ng 18 V-League: N\u00f3ng cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua tr\u1ee5 h\u1ea1ng, HAGL c\u00f3 th\u00eam chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/22/truoc-vong-18-vleague-nong-cuoc-dua-tru-hang-hagl-co-them-chien-thang.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Khi m\u00e0 V-League \u0111ang \u0111i v\u00e0o nh\u1eefng v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i th\u00ec cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua tr\u1ee5 h\u1ea1ng \u0111ang tr\u1edf n\u00ean n\u00f3ng h\u01a1n bao gi\u1edd h\u1ebft. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, CLB HAGL c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i gi\u00e0nh 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 g\u1eb7p Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a.</h2><h2>N\u00f3ng cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua tr\u1ee5 h\u1ea1ng</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau khi SLNA c\u00f3 c\u00fa b\u1ee9t t\u1ed1p ngo\u1ea1n m\u1ee5c b\u1eb1ng chu\u1ed7i 5 th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp, l\u00fac n\u00e0y cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua tr\u1ee5 h\u1ea1ng V-League 2018 \u0111ang l\u00e0 cu\u1ed9c c\u1ea1nh tranh c\u1ee7a 4 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1 (17 \u0111i\u1ec3m), S\u00e0i G\u00f2n, Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh (c\u00f9ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 16 \u0111i\u1ec3m) v\u00e0 CLB TP.HCM (15 \u0111i\u1ec3m).</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Khi m\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111ang b\u00e1m s\u00e1t nhau nh\u01b0 v\u1eady, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i nh\u1eefng c\u00fa v\u1ea5p ng\u00e3 trong giai \u0111o\u1ea1n c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 khi\u1ebfn c\u1ee5c di\u1ec7n cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua tr\u1ee5 h\u1ea1ng thay \u0111\u1ed5i.</p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede v\u00f2ng n\u00e0y, \u0111\u1ed9i cu\u1ed1i b\u1ea3ng TP.HCM s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi th\u1eed th\u00e1ch mang t\u00ean CLB H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i t\u1ea1i H\u00e0ng \u0110\u1eaby. H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i l\u00fac n\u00e0y \u0111ang d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u BXH v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t phong \u0111\u1ed9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng. Do \u0111\u00f3 s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd n\u1ebfu h\u1ecd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a HLV Miura \u0111\u1ec3 duy tr\u00ec kho\u1ea3ng c\u00e1ch 16 \u0111i\u1ec3m v\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 b\u00e1m \u0111u\u1ed5i.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00f2ng 18 V-League N\u00f3ng cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua tr\u1ee5 h\u1ea1ng, HAGL s\u1ebd c\u00f3 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00f2ng 18 V-League N\u00f3ng cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua tr\u1ee5 h\u1ea1ng, HAGL s\u1ebd c\u00f3 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/6/Truoc-vong-18-V-League-Nong-cuoc-dua-tru-hang,-HAGL-se-co-3-diem-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>CLB TP.HCM c\u00f3 chuy\u1ebfn l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ea7y kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n t\u1edbi s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede v\u00f2ng 18 V-League 2018, c\u1ea3 Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh v\u00e0 S\u00e0i G\u00f2n \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0. Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh g\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111ang c\u00f3 phong \u0111\u1ed9 r\u1ea5t cao trong th\u1eddi gian g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 SLNA, trong khi S\u00e0i G\u00f2n g\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00ec b\u1ea3ng FLC Thanh H\u00f3a. V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec1u m\u1ea1nh h\u01a1n h\u1eb3n, c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a c\u1ea3 Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh v\u00e0 S\u00e0i G\u00f2n \u0111\u1ec1u l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t nh\u1ecf.\u00a0</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">CLB XSKT C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1 c\u0169ng kh\u00f3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec3m \u1edf v\u00f2ng n\u00e0y khi ph\u1ea3i di chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi C\u1ea9m Ph\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch tr\u01b0\u1edbc CLB Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh. S\u00e2n nh\u00e0 lu\u00f4n l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec3m t\u1ef1a \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a HLV Phan Thanh H\u00f9ng gi\u00e0nh nh\u1eefng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y. V\u00e0 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn h\u1ecd s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i gia t\u0103ng \u0111i\u1ec3m s\u1ed1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1ed9t C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1 \u0111ang trong th\u1eddi k\u1ef3 kh\u1ee7ng ho\u1ea3ng.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">4 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng cu\u1ed1i b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec1u g\u1eb7p nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 r\u1ea5t m\u1ea1nh \u1edf v\u00f2ng 18 V-League 2018. V\u00e0 nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng cho c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u1edf nh\u00f3m n\u00e0y trong lo\u1ea1t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u di\u1ec5n ra cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y.</p>\r\n<h2>HAGL c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i gi\u00e0nh 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 18 V-League, CLB HAGL s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u01a1i tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 Pleiku g\u1eb7p CLB Sanna Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a, \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 m\u00e0 h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i m\u00f9a b\u00f3ng n\u0103m nay.\u00a0</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f2n nh\u1edb \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u00f3, t\u01b0\u1edfng nh\u01b0 HAGL \u0111\u00e3 su\u00fdt gi\u00e0nh 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m t\u1ea1i ph\u1ed1 Bi\u1ec3n th\u00ec tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i Nguy\u1ec5n V\u0103n Ki\u00ean \u0111\u00e3 cho Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u01b0\u1edfng qu\u1ea3 penalty t\u01b0\u1edfng t\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u1edf nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i, khi\u1ebfn tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u k\u1ebft th\u00fac v\u1edbi k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 h\u00f2a 1-1.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Khanh Hoa vs HAL\" title=\"Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a vs HAL\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/6/truc-tiep-khanh-hoa-vs-hagl-18h00-ngay-65-vleague-2018.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>\u00a0HAGL c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i 'b\u00e1o th\u00f9' sau tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a \u1ea5m \u1ee9c \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1ea5t \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ea7y ti\u1ebfc nu\u1ed1i \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i, ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111ang r\u1ea5t quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m 'b\u00e1o th\u00f9' \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1 khi h\u1ecd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0. Tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Pleiku, HAGL m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ec3 thua \u0111\u00fang 1 tr\u1eadn \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y.\u00a0</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00ec th\u1ebf, n\u1ebfu thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u00fang phong \u0111\u1ed9 v\u00e0 h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf nh\u1eefng sai l\u1ea7m c\u1ee7a h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 HAGL ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 quy\u1ec1n m\u01a1 m\u1ed9ng t\u1edbi tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng th\u1ee9 7 \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y, qua \u0111\u00f3 t\u00edch l\u0169y \u0111i\u1ec3m s\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ec3 b\u00e1m s\u00e1t t\u1ed1p 3 tr\u00ean BXH.</p>\r\n<h2>H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i b\u0103ng b\u0103ng v\u1ec1 \u0111\u00edch</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">CLB H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i \u0111ang ph\u00f4 di\u1ec5n m\u1ed9t s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh v\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1ed9i c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i t\u1ea1i V-League. T\u00ednh \u0111\u1ebfn tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ee9 18, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Chu \u0110\u00ecnh Nghi\u00eam \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 t\u1edbi 14 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng, ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ec3 h\u00f2a 2 v\u00e0 thua 1.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng n\u00e0y gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4 \u0111ang b\u0103ng b\u0103ng v\u1ec1 \u0111\u00edch v\u1edbi 16 \u0111i\u1ec3m nhi\u00eau h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111ang \u0111\u1ee9ng th\u1ee9 2 l\u00e0 Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u1ebfu ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c duy tr\u00ec m\u1ea1ch th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch s\u1edbm ngay \u1edf v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ee9 19, \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00e0 r\u1ea5t \u00edt \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u1ec9 ph\u1ea3i g\u1eb7p m\u1ed9t TP.HCM \u0111ang tr\u00ean b\u1edd v\u1ef1c r\u1edbt h\u1ea1ng, CLB H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n t\u1ef1 tin gi\u00e0nh 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m. S\u00e2n nh\u00e0 H\u00e0ng \u0110\u1eaby ch\u01b0a t\u1eebng ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn m\u1ed9t th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i n\u00e0o c\u1ee7a V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y. V\u00ec th\u1ebf nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u1edf v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1edbi.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ngo\u00e0i c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u k\u1ec3 tr\u00ean, t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 18 V-League c\u00f2n di\u1ec5n ra c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng vs H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng v\u00e0 Qu\u1ea3ng Nam vs B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng. Bongda24h s\u1ebd c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn, k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y. M\u1eddi b\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ecdc ch\u00fa \u00fd \u0111\u00f3n xem.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Lich thi dau vong 18 V-League\" title=\"L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00f2ng 18 V-League\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/6/Lich-thi-dau-vong-18-V-League-2018.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00f2ng 18 V-League</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/sao-hagl-nhan-giai-thuong-ban-thang-dep-nhat-vleague-trong-thang-6-168-190503.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/22/sao-hagl-nhan-giai-thuong-ban-thang-dep-nhat-vleague-trong-thang-6.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/sao-hagl-nhan-giai-thuong-ban-thang-dep-nhat-vleague-trong-thang-6-168-190503.html\">Sao HAGL nh\u1eadn gi\u1ea3i th\u01b0\u1edfng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u1eb9p nh\u1ea5t V-League trong th\u00e1ng 6</span><br>\r\nTi\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Tr\u1ea7n Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c VPF trao gi\u1ea3i th\u01b0\u1edfng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u1eb9p nh\u1ea5t th\u00e1ng 6 sau pha s\u00fat ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1eb9p m\u1eaft l\u00e0m rung l\u01b0\u1edbi nh\u00e0 \u0110KV\u0110 Qu\u1ea3ng Nam t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 13...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-duong-minh-ninh-tiec-nuoi-sau-tran-hoa-cua-hagl-truoc-quang-nam-168-190172.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/17/hlv-duong-minh-ninh-tiec-nuoi-sau-tran-hoa-cua-hagl-truoc-quang-nam.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-duong-minh-ninh-tiec-nuoi-sau-tran-hoa-cua-hagl-truoc-quang-nam-168-190172.html\">HLV D\u01b0\u01a1ng Minh Ninh ti\u1ebfc nu\u1ed1i sau tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a c\u1ee7a HAGL tr\u01b0\u1edbc Qu\u1ea3ng Nam</span><br>\r\nPh\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, HLV D\u01b0\u01a1ng Minh Ninh \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ecf ra ti\u1ebfc nu\u1ed1i khi c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 ch\u1ec9 gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m d\u00f9 h\u1ecd m\u1edbi ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/tran-dau/quang-ninh-vs-ha-noi-vong-17-vleague-2018-372-190090.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/1/tong-hop-quang-ninh-12-ha-noi-vong-17-vleague-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/tran-dau/quang-ninh-vs-ha-noi-vong-17-vleague-2018-372-190090.html\">Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh 1-2 H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i (KT): Ch\u01a1i tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ea5t M\u1ecf v\u1eabn kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 b\u00e1o th\u00f9</span><br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c m\u1ed9t m\u00ecnh m\u1ed9t ng\u1ef1a trong cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua t\u1edbi ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch khi gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 2-1 \u1edf v\u00f2ng 17 Nuti Caf\u00e9 V-League chi\u1ec1u 1/7.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)</p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"960","checkdouble":"190525"},{"date":"17:33 06/07","title":"5 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 2 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i n\u1ebfu Ronaldo t\u1edbi Juventus","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/6/5-nguoi-chien-thang-va-2-nguoi-that-bai-neu-ronaldo-toi-juventus.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Cristiano Ronaldo t\u1edbi Juventus l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t cao, d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 5 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 2 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i n\u1ebfu CR7 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ea7u qu\u00e2n cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Turin.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng: Cristiano Ronaldo</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nCristiano Ronaldo r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u01b0\u1edfng l\u1ee3i n\u1ebfu c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Juventus. \u0110\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, anh s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u01b0\u1edfng m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u00e0 m\u00ecnh mong mu\u1ed1n, \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00e0 Real Madrid \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng cho ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"5 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 2 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i n\u1ebfu Ronaldo t\u1edbi Juventus h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"5 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 2 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i n\u1ebfu Ronaldo t\u1edbi Juventus h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/6/5-nguoi-chien-thang-va-2-nguoi-that-bai-neu-Ronaldo-toi-Juventus-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Ronaldo h\u01b0\u1edfng l\u1ee3i n\u1ebfu t\u1edbi Juventus</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTh\u1ee9 hai, trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Juventus, t\u1ea7m quan tr\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a Ronaldo s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3. Anh s\u1ebd l\u00e0 t\u00e2m \u0111i\u1ec3m v\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng, l\u00e0 t\u00e2m \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng v\u00e0 thu h\u00fat s\u1ef1 ch\u00fa \u00fd c\u1ee7a \u0111\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ea3o NHM.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTh\u1ee9 ba, Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u ri\u00eang cho m\u00ecnh, tho\u00e1t kh\u1ecfi s\u1ef1 c\u1ea1nh tranh \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb Leo Messi. CR7 ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 2 danh hi\u1ec7u La Liga trong 9 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Real, trong th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u00f3 M10 c\u00f3 t\u1edbi 6 l\u1ea7n l\u00ean ng\u00f4i c\u00f9ng Barca.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nCu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng, Ronaldo c\u1ea7n th\u00eam nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u \u1edf Serie A \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u1edf n\u00ean v\u0129 \u0111\u1ea1i. N\u1ebfu c\u00f9ng Juventus gi\u00e0nh th\u00eam nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u l\u1edbn, anh s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1edb \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 v\u0129 \u0111\u1ea1i nh\u1ea5t trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi thua cu\u1ed9c: Gonzalo Higuain</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ronaldo v\u00e0 Higuain g\u1eafn b\u00f3 c\u00f9ng nhau trong 4 n\u0103m t\u1ea1i Real Madrid, t\u1eeb n\u0103m 2009 \u0111\u1ebfn n\u0103m 2013. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina sau \u0111\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea1nh tranh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1ecb tr\u00ed v\u1edbi Karim Benzema v\u00e0 bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea7u qu\u00e2n cho Napoli.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Higuain se lai nhuong san khau cho Ronaldo\" title=\"Higuain s\u1ebd l\u1ea1i nh\u01b0\u1eddng s\u00e2n kh\u1ea5u cho Ronaldo\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/6/higuain.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Higuain s\u1ebd l\u1ea1i nh\u01b0\u1eddng s\u00e2n kh\u1ea5u cho Ronaldo</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n Higuain b\u1eadt kh\u1ecfi Real l\u00e0 b\u1edfi anh kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn l\u00e0m n\u1ec1n cho Ronaldo, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1987 mu\u1ed1n d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m khi c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i thay v\u00ec l\u00e0m t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng \u0111\u01b0a b\u00f3ng cho CR7. Higuain kh\u00f4ng l\u00e0m \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 nh\u01b0ng Benzema th\u00ec c\u00f3, v\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t gi\u1eefa hai c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Juventus, Higuain \u0111ang l\u00e0 ng\u00f4i sao \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng, anh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eafc \u0111\u1ebfn m\u1ed7i khi Juventus chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng ho\u1eb7c th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i \u1edf nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u quan tr\u1ecdng.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a Ronaldo, s\u1ef1 ch\u00fa \u00fd s\u1ebd d\u1ed3n sang CR7. N\u1ebfu Higuain ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn \u1edf l\u1ea1i Juventus, anh s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c l\u00e0m n\u1ec1n cho si\u00eau sao 33 tu\u1ed5i.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTh\u1eadm ch\u00ed Higuain c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ec3 nh\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u1ed7 cho Mario Mandzukic, m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 thi\u00ean h\u01b0\u1edbng ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 nh\u01b0 Benzema \u1edf Real Madrid.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng: Isco v\u00e0 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb c\u1ee7a Real</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi c\u00e1i b\u00f3ng qu\u00e1 l\u1edbn c\u1ee7a Ronaldo, c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ra s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Isco v\u00e0 nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb c\u1ee7a Real Madrid nh\u01b0 Asensio kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u. Tuy nhi\u00ean, h\u1ecd s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trao nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i h\u01a1n khi CR7 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n hi\u1ec7n di\u1ec7n \u1edf s\u00e2n Bernabeu n\u1eefa.&nbsp;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Isco va Asensio co the duoc trao nhieu co hoi hon o mua giai toi\" title=\"Isco v\u00e0 Asensio c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trao nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i h\u01a1n \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/6/isco.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Isco v\u00e0 Asensio c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trao nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i h\u01a1n \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nSau khi Andres Iniesta chia tay T\u00e2y Ban Nha, Isco \u0111ang tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh ng\u00f4i sao m\u1edbi c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 B\u00f2 t\u00f3t. Anh mu\u1ed1n \u0111i\u1ec1u t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 x\u1ea3y ra \u1edf Real Madrid khi Ronaldo \u0111\u1ea7u qu\u00e2n cho Juventus, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng n\u00e0y ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 x\u1ea3y ra khi Isco c\u00f3 m\u1ed1i quan h\u1ec7 th\u00e2n thi\u1ebft v\u1edbi t\u00e2n HLV Lopetegui.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nKhi Isco \u0111\u1ebfn Real, anh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u. Tuy nhi\u00ean, v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a Ronaldo c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1992 ch\u01b0a bao gi\u1edd tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf \u1edf s\u00e2n Bernabeu. Tuy nhi\u00ean, m\u00f9a t\u1edbi c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ea7m quan tr\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a anh s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u00e2ng l\u00ean m\u1ed9t t\u1ea7m cao m\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-tbn/tiet-lo-ronaldo-da-ky-hop-dong-voi-juventus-180-190431.html\" target=\"_blank\">Cristiano Ronaldo t\u1edbi Juventus</span> s\u1ebd m\u1edf ra c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 Marco Asensio v\u00e0 Dani Ceballos. V\u1edbi Isco thay th\u1ebf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u1ee7a Ronaldo, Ceballos v\u00e0 Asensio c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u1ebf ch\u1ed7 v\u1ecb tr\u00ed cho ch\u00ednh Isco \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng: Paulo Dybala</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Paulo Dybala l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o v\u00f4 h\u1ea1n, \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Palermo. Tuy nhi\u00ean, \u1edf Juventus, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o c\u1ee7a Dybala ch\u01b0a \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e1t huy t\u1ed1i \u0111a b\u1edfi Gonzalo Higuain kh\u00f4ng k\u1ebft th\u00fac qu\u00e1 t\u1ed1t nh\u1eefng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i do c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y t\u1ea1o ra.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Kha nang sang tao cua Dybala se duoc phat huy toi da voi su co mat cua Ronaldo\" title=\"Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o c\u1ee7a Dybala s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e1t huy t\u1ed1i \u0111a v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a Ronaldo\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/6/dybala.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o c\u1ee7a Dybala s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e1t huy t\u1ed1i \u0111a v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a Ronaldo</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, m\u1ed9t m\u00ecnh Dybala \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o ra t\u1edbi 18 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho Higuain, nh\u01b0ng ch\u1ec9 2 trong s\u1ed1 \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chuy\u1ec3n h\u00f3a th\u00e0nh b\u00e0n th\u1eafng. M\u00f9a t\u1edbi, v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 hi\u1ec7n di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Ronaldo, ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e1t huy t\u1ed1i \u0111a.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nDybala ghi t\u1edbi 22 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u1edf Serie A m\u00f9a v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i, nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n c\u1ea3 Higuain (16). Tuy nhi\u00ean, ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1993 ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 5 \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o. M\u00f9a t\u1edbi, nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ed1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a anh s\u1ebd gi\u1ea3m \u0111i c\u00f2n s\u1ed1 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o s\u1ebd t\u0103ng l\u00ean tr\u00f4ng th\u1ea5y b\u1edfi s\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a Ronaldo.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi thua cu\u1ed9c: Tottenham</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi s\u1ef1 ra \u0111i c\u1ee7a Ronaldo, Real Madrid s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t ng\u00f4i sao l\u1edbn. Karim Benzema n\u0103m nay \u0111\u00e3 31 tu\u1ed5i, anh kh\u00f4ng duy tr\u00ec phong \u0111\u1ed9 ghi b\u00e0n qu\u00e1 t\u1ed1t trong nh\u1eefng m\u00f9a g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Real co the mua Harry Kane o He 2018\" title=\"Real c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 mua Harry Kane \u1edf H\u00e8 2018\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/6/tot.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Real c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 mua Harry Kane \u1edf H\u00e8 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nLos Blancos s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018, m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00e0 h\u1ecd nh\u1eafm t\u1edbi l\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Harry Kane c\u1ee7a Tottenham.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong nh\u1eefng m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, Kane duy tr\u00ec phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ef1c cao. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng ch\u00e2n s\u00fat xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 25 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 ghi 135 b\u00e0n sau 187 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n cho Tottenham.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTottenham v\u1eeba gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1993, song kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Real mua Harry Kane th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng l\u00e0 v\u1eabn c\u00f2n. N\u1ebfu h\u1ecd chi ra m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n kh\u1ed5ng l\u1ed3 v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng cho ng\u00f4i sao 25 tu\u1ed5i m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ef1c cao, Spurs ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 nh\u1ea3 ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9 Tottenham \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eebng tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n Gareth Bale v\u00e0 Luka Modric cho Real, nh\u01b0ng r\u1ed3i s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n c\u1ef1c l\u1edbn m\u00e0 Los Blancos \u0111\u01b0a ra khi\u1ebfn Spurs kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 c\u01b0\u1ee1ng l\u1ea1i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng: Gareth Bale</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede Real Madrid, hi\u1ebfm khi Ronaldo v\u00e0 Bale t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng c\u00f9ng nhau. B\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i n\u00e0y ch\u01a1i kh\u00e1 c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n, b\u1edfi v\u1eady h\u1ecd th\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u1ecdn c\u00e1ch d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m khi c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i thay v\u00ec ph\u1ed1i h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Bale se quyet tam chung to minh khi Ronaldo ra di\" title=\"Bale s\u1ebd quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf m\u00ecnh khi Ronaldo ra \u0111i\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/6/bale.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Bale s\u1ebd quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf m\u00ecnh khi Ronaldo ra \u0111i</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nKhi Bale v\u00e0 Ronaldo c\u00f9ng c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t tr\u00ean s\u00e2n, nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u m\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi x\u1ee9 Wales lu m\u1edd CR7 l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t hi\u1ebfm, b\u1edfi l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a Real Madrid ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 ch\u1ee9 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1989.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nKhi Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 ra \u0111i v\u00e0 Lopetegui \u0111\u1ebfn, t\u1ea7m \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a Bale c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3. R\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha s\u1ebd s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 4-3-3 v\u1edbi Isco b\u00ean c\u00e1nh tr\u00e1i c\u00f2n Bale ch\u01a1i b\u00ean c\u00e1nh ph\u1ea3i.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nKhi \u0111\u00e3 tho\u00e1t kh\u1ecfi c\u00e1i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Ronaldo, Bale \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd b\u00f9ng n\u1ed5 m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd. M\u00f9a t\u1edbi, ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u1ef1c thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a c\u1ef1u sao Tottenham s\u1ebd l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng: Serie A</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">La Liga \u0111\u00e3 m\u1ea5t \u0111i m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i ni\u1ec1m vui \u0111\u1ebfn v\u1edbi Serie A khi h\u1ecd s\u1edf h\u1eefu m\u1ed9t si\u00eau sao c\u1ee1 b\u1ef1 v\u00e0 thu h\u00fat \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m c\u1ee7a h\u00e0ng tri\u1ec7u NHM tr\u00ean kh\u1eafp th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Sersie A vui mung khi don mot ngoi sao nhu Ronaldo\" title=\"Sersie A vui m\u1eebng khi \u0111\u00f3n m\u1ed9t ng\u00f4i sao nh\u01b0 Ronaldo\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/6/serie-a.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Sersie A vui m\u1eebng khi \u0111\u00f3n m\u1ed9t ng\u00f4i sao nh\u01b0 Ronaldo</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong nh\u1eefng m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, Serie A kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 ti\u1ec1m n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a nhi\u1ec1u ng\u00f4i sao. Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 gi\u1ecfi t\u1eeb gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y chuy\u1ec3n sang thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf Ph\u00e1p, Anh hay T\u00e2y Ban Nha. \u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 khi\u1ebfn ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 s\u1ef1 c\u1ea1nh tranh c\u1ee7a gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1ea3m \u0111i \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nS\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a Ronaldo nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t l\u00e0n gi\u00f3 m\u1edbi th\u1ed5i v\u00e0o gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u, n\u00f3 gi\u00fap Serie A \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u00fa \u00fd nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n. V\u00e0 r\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 sau s\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a CR7 nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi s\u1ebd c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Serie A \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed1i tr\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a Juventus v\u00e0 si\u00eau sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n*Squawka.com</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"959","checkdouble":"190526"},{"date":"10:54 06/07","title":"\u0110\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng Ph\u00e1p: \"Pogba l\u00e0 th\u1ee7 l\u0129nh \u0111\u00edch th\u1ef1c\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/6/Lionel-Messi-muon-Barca-mua-Paul-Pogba-cua-MU-hinh-anh.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>V\u00e0o t\u1ed1i nay, Ph\u00e1p s\u1ebd quy\u1ebft chi\u1ebfn v\u1edbi Uruguay cho m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfc v\u00e9 v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft. Trong bu\u1ed5i ph\u1ecfng v\u1ea5n g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t, th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Lloris ca ng\u1ee3i Pogba c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111em v\u1ec1 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng.\r\n</h2><h2>Pogba l\u00e0 th\u1ee7 l\u0129nh \u0111\u00edch th\u1ef1c<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u0103m nay, b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 89 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 hay nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a tuy\u1ec3n Ph\u00e1p. \u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u01a1i b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh m\u00e1y qu\u00e9t Kante, Paul Pogba tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh \u0111\u00edch th\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, v\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3ng vai tr\u00f2 ch\u00ednh trong c\u00e1c ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a G\u00e0 tr\u1ed1ng Gaulois.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh t\u00e0i n\u0103ng n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt, vai tr\u00f2, t\u1ea7m \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a Pogba c\u0169ng quan tr\u1ecdng h\u01a1n theo n\u0103m th\u00e1ng. M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng Hugo Lloris \u0111\u00e3 ca ng\u1ee3i ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 M.U tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u00e1nh quan tr\u1ecdng v\u1edbi Uruguay:<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh, Pogba \u0111ang ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n v\u01b0\u1ee3t b\u1eadc. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111ang t\u00edch l\u0169y kinh nghi\u1ec7m t\u1ea1i Man United, tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 Juventus, v\u00e0 b\u00e2y gi\u1edd c\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u trong nhi\u1ec1u m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i, nhi\u1ec1u tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u0169ng \u0111ang ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ea7m \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng trong ph\u00f2ng thay \u0111\u1ed3. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t t\u00edn hi\u1ec7u t\u00edch c\u1ef1c, b\u1edfi Pogba l\u00e0 th\u1ee7 l\u0129nh \u0111\u00edch th\u1ef1c, m\u1ed9t nh\u00e0 l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o thi\u00ean b\u1ea9m.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Hugo Lloris ca ng\u1ee3i Pogba c\u00f3 t\u1ed5 ch\u1ea5t th\u1ee7 l\u0129nh\" title=\"Pogba\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/6/Lionel-Messi-muon-Barca-mua-Paul-Pogba-cua-MU-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Hugo Lloris ca ng\u1ee3i Pogba c\u00f3 t\u1ed5 ch\u1ea5t th\u1ee7 l\u0129nh</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;Pogba l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ea7y tham v\u1ecdng, t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 ch\u00fang ta \u0111\u1ec1u bi\u1ebft c\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 t\u00e0i n\u0103ng, c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ec3 cung c\u1ea5p cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng v\u00e0 nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi thi \u0111\u1ea5u xung quanh m\u00ecnh. World Cup l\u00e0 gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ec9nh cao, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7, v\u00e0 t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 Pogba l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong s\u1ed1 \u0111\u00f3.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ngo\u00e0i ra, Hugo Lloris c\u0169ng l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng \u0111\u1ec1 cao t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a sao tr\u1ebb Mbappe, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e3 g\u00f3p c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap nh\u1ea5n ch\u00ecm \u0110T Argentina \u1edf v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1edbc. Tuy nhi\u00ean, th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p cho r\u1eb1ng Mbappe v\u1eabn ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 nh\u01b0 v\u1eady, ch\u01a1i \u0111\u00fang phong c\u00e1ch nh\u01b0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0 t\u1eadn h\u01b0\u1edfng nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng, thay v\u00ec th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n k\u1ef9 n\u0103ng c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c Lloris ca ng\u1ee3i Pogba, ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a Ph\u1ea5p r\u1ea5t hy v\u1ecdng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 n\u00e0y \u0111em v\u1ec1 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng. V\u00e0o t\u1ed1i nay, h\u1ecd s\u1ebd ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n \u0110T Uruguay \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh l\u1ea5y chi\u1ebfc v\u00e9 l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/hlv-uruguay-noi-gi-ve-chan-thuong-cua-cavani-421-190472.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/6/tho-world-cup-tu-ket-bi-braxin.PNG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/hlv-uruguay-noi-gi-ve-chan-thuong-cua-cavani-421-190472.html\">HLV Uruguay n\u00f3i g\u00ec v\u1ec1 ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a Cavani?</span><br>\r\nHLV Oscar Tabarez n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 Edison Cavani, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y 71 tu\u1ed5i kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o PSG v\u1eabn b\u1ecf ng\u1ecf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ra s\u00e2n trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Ph\u00e1p.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nhan-dinh-uruguay-vs-phap-21h-ngay-67-thu-manh-co-lai-cong-khung-421-190467.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/6/Nhan-dinh-Uruguay-vs-Phap-(21h-ngay-67)-tu-ket-World-Cup-2018-hinh-anh.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nhan-dinh-uruguay-vs-phap-21h-ngay-67-thu-manh-co-lai-cong-khung-421-190467.html\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Uruguay vs Ph\u00e1p (21h ng\u00e0y 6/7): Th\u1ee7 m\u1ea1nh c\u00f3 l\u1ea1i c\u00f4ng kh\u1ee7ng?</span><br>\r\nNh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Uruguay vs Ph\u00e1p s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t th\u00fa v\u1ecb khi hai \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f3 phong c\u00e1ch kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 nhau. Tuy nhi\u00ean, n\u1ebfu \u0111i v\u00e0o chi ti\u1ebft, s\u1ebd th\u1ea5y gi\u1eefa \u0111\u00f4i b\u00ean v\u1eabn c\u00f3 kh\u00e1c...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"958","checkdouble":"190478"},{"date":"10:30 06/07","title":"Sao tuy\u1ec3n Anh: \"Colombia l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 b\u1ea9n nh\u1ea5t t\u00f4i t\u1eebng bi\u1ebft\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/6/cac-ngoi-sao-bong-da-nhung-nguoi-truyen-cam-hung.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>D\u00f9 \u0111\u00e3 l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft, nh\u01b0ng \u0110T Anh c\u00f3 v\u1ebb v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a h\u1ebft kh\u00f3 ch\u1ecbu sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i. M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, trung v\u1ec7 John Stones ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch \u0110T Colombia v\u00ec l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i \u0111\u1ea7y ti\u1ec3u x\u1ea3o.\r\n</h2><h2>Colombia l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng &ldquo;b\u1ea9n th\u1ec9u&rdquo; nh\u1ea5t<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u1ecb trung v\u1ec7 Yerry Mina g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i sau khi d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u1edd qu\u1ea3 ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n c\u1ee7a Harry kane, Tam S\u01b0 ph\u1ea3i tr\u1ea3i qua lo\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ea5u s\u00fang m\u1edbi h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7. Su\u1ed1t c\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn, Colombia li\u00ean t\u1ee5c ph\u1ea1m l\u1ed7i v\u1edbi c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0110T Anh, khi nh\u1eadn t\u1edbi 6 th\u1ebb v\u00e0ng, t\u1ea1o ra tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u gi\u00e0u k\u1ecbch t\u00ednh, nh\u01b0ng c\u0169ng r\u1ea5t b\u1ea1o l\u1ef1c.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y, m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y trung v\u1ec7 John Stones cho bi\u1ebft: &ldquo;Colombia c\u00f3 l\u1ebd l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng b\u1ea9n th\u1ec9u nh\u1ea5t m\u00e0 t\u00f4i t\u1eebng \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u. Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1eadt k\u1ef3 l\u1ea1. Khi ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u01b0\u1edfng qu\u1ea3 ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n, b\u1ecdn h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 bao v\u00e2y tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f2n \u0111\u1ea9y \u00f4ng \u1ea5y. Ngo\u00e0i ra c\u00f2n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1eefng pha ph\u1ea1m l\u1ed7i th\u00f4 b\u1ea1o kh\u00e1c m\u00e0 t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec1u ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Stones ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch \u0110T Colombia v\u00ec l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i th\u00f4 b\u1ea1o\" title=\"Stones\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/6/cac-ngoi-sao-bong-da-nhung-nguoi-truyen-cam-hung.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Stones ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch \u0110T Colombia v\u00ec l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i th\u00f4 b\u1ea1o</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;C\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u \u0111i\u1ec1u ti\u00eau c\u1ef1c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c phun ra t\u1eeb mi\u1ec7ng c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Colombia, m\u00e0 t\u00f4i ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n ch\u01b0a t\u1eebng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nghe \u0111\u1ebfn. Ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3, nh\u01b0ng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ea3n l\u0129nh v\u00e0 tinh th\u1ea7n chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng b\u1ecb cu\u1ed1n v\u00e0o \u00e2m m\u01b0u c\u1ee7a Colombia, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ch\u1ec9 mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u00e1nh nhau v\u00e0 ch\u1eedi b\u1edbi ch\u00fang t\u00f4i.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;\u0110T Anh c\u0169ng m\u1eafc k\u1eb9t trong nh\u1eefng k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, nh\u01b0ng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua b\u1eb1ng c\u00e1ch ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t d\u1ea5u hi\u1ec7u tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi m\u00e0 \u0110T Anh \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o ra, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n, nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00e3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o v\u1ec1 \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">John Stones ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c: &ldquo;T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 chia s\u1ebb ngay t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u gi\u1ea3i, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup. \u0110\u00e3 qu\u00e1 l\u00e2u r\u1ed3i k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb khi n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh l\u00ean ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch, v\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 ph\u1ea3i t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111ang ti\u1ebfn th\u00eam m\u1ed9t b\u01b0\u1edbc g\u1ea7n h\u01a1n t\u1edbi \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3, nh\u01b0ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc ti\u00ean c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n \u0111\u00e3.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec Stones ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch \u0110T Colombia, c\u00f3 l\u1ebd Tam S\u01b0 s\u1ebd l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch k\u1ef9 tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00f2ng t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft. Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n c\u0169ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 kh\u00f3 ch\u1ecbu trong ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1, v\u00e0 ch\u01b0a bi\u1ebft ch\u1eebng s\u1ebd g\u00e2y ra kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n l\u1edbn v\u1edbi tuy\u1ec3n Anh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/vi-ly-do-nay-tuyen-anh-chap-nhan-mang-tieng-kich-si-421-190462.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/6/vi-ly-do-nay-tuyen-anh-chap-nhan-mang-tieng-kich-si.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/vi-ly-do-nay-tuyen-anh-chap-nhan-mang-tieng-kich-si-421-190462.html\">V\u00ec l\u00fd do n\u00e0y, tuy\u1ec3n Anh ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn mang ti\u1ebfng &ldquo;k\u1ecbch s\u0129&rdquo;</span><br>\r\nKieran Trippier ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 \u0110T Anh. H\u1eadu v\u1ec7 n\u00e0y tin r\u1eb1ng Tam s\u01b0 hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 kh\u00f4n ngoan h\u01a1n so v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1edbn g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y h\u1ecd tham d\u1ef1.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/tu-ket-world-cup-2018-hay-de-y-nguoi-anh-421-190417.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/5/tu-ket-world-cup-2018-hay-de-y-nguoi-anh.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/tu-ket-world-cup-2018-hay-de-y-nguoi-anh-421-190417.html\">T\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup 2018: H\u00e3y \u0111\u1ec3 \u00fd ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh</span><br>\r\nT\u1eeb m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ch\u1eb3ng ai quan t\u00e2m, \u0110T Anh t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 \u0111ang c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i l\u1ecbch s\u1eed \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00e0m n\u00ean \u0111i\u1ec1u k\u1ef3 di\u1ec7u, sau khi \u0111\u00e3 l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"957","checkdouble":"190479"},{"date":"10:01 06/07","title":"Juventus l\u00e0 b\u01b0\u1edbc l\u00f9i s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ee7a Ronaldo","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/5/juventus-la-buoc-lui-su-nghiep-cua-ronaldo.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Barca mua Paul Pogba c\u1ee7a MU l\u00e0 mong mu\u1ed1n c\u1ee7a si\u00eau sao Lionel Messi, M10 mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 \u00edt nh\u1ea5t m\u1ed9t ng\u00f4i sao l\u1edbn \u1edf H\u00e8 2018.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Messi mu\u1ed1n Barca chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Pogba</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nAntoine Griezmann l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a Barca \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018, song ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Catalan v\u00e0 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Atletico Madrid.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Lionel Messi mu\u1ed1n Barca mua Paul Pogba c\u1ee7a MU h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Lionel Messi mu\u1ed1n Barca mua Paul Pogba c\u1ee7a MU h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/6/Lionel-Messi-muon-Barca-mua-Paul-Pogba-cua-MU-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Messi mu\u1ed1n Barca mua Pogba</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1ed3 h\u1ee5t Griezmann ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn khi\u1ebfn Barca c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng, h\u1ecd v\u1eabn mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t ng\u00f4i sao l\u1edbn \u1edf H\u00e8 2018. Barca mua Paul Pogba c\u1ee7a MU l\u00e0 mong mu\u1ed1n c\u1ee7a si\u00eau sao Lionel Messi, M10 mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 31 tu\u1ed5i.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMessi hi\u1ec3u r\u1eb1ng s\u1ef1 ra \u0111i c\u1ee7a Iniesta khi\u1ebfn s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh n\u01a1i tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa c\u1ee7a Barca b\u1ecb suy gi\u1ea3m \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina mu\u1ed1n n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa b\u1eb1ng m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 kh\u1ee7ng v\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n Barca mua ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a M.U.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p Pogba t\u1edbi Camp Nou, anh s\u1ebd gi\u00fap Philippe Coutinho \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1 cao h\u01a1n, qua \u0111\u00f3 gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ee1 cho Messi \u1edf nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ngo\u00e0i Barca th\u00ec Real c\u0169ng quan t\u00e2m Pogba, h\u1ecd nh\u1eafm c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 25 tu\u1ed5i nh\u01b0 s\u1ef1 thay th\u1ebf l\u00e2u d\u00e0i cho Luka Modric, ng\u01b0\u1eddi n\u0103m nay \u0111\u00e3 b\u01b0\u1edbc sang tu\u1ed5i 33.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Kh\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 \u0111\u1ec3 Barca chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Pogba</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Don Balon kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c M.U b\u00e1n Pogba, Barca ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi t\u1edbi 100 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf ph\u1ea3i b\u1ecf ra 89.5 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p t\u1eeb Juventus.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Paul Pogba cua M.U\" title=\"Paul Pogba cua M.U\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/3/bat-chap-mau-thuan-voi-mourinho-pogba-se-o-lai-mu.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>MU s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 nh\u1ea3 Paul Pogba cho Barca</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua gi\u1eefa Mourinho v\u00e0 Pogba \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n m\u00e2u thu\u1eabn, \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 khi\u1ebfn c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1993 chia tay s\u00e2n Old Trafford \u1edf H\u00e8 2018.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, Mourinho kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u00f4ng s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 Pogba ra \u0111i v\u1edbi b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 gi\u00e1 n\u00e0o. \u00d4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p n\u1eb1m trong k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nB\u1ea3n th\u00e2n Pogba c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n g\u1eafn b\u00f3 v\u1edbi M.U, anh c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y h\u00e0o h\u1ee9ng khi Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 Fred. V\u1edbi s\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a t\u00e2n binh ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Pogba s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ea9y l\u00ean \u0111\u00e1 cao h\u01a1n \u1edf m\u00f9a t\u1edbi, nh\u1eb1m t\u1eadp trung v\u00e0o nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"956","checkdouble":"190480"},{"date":"09:37 06/07","title":"HLV Southgate: \"B\u00e2y gi\u1edd ho\u1eb7c kh\u00f4ng bao gi\u1edd cho \u0110T Anh\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/4/hlv-southgate-bay-gio-hoac-khong-bao-gio-cho-dt-anh.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u hi\u1ec7u tri\u1ec7u tinh th\u1ea7n c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n 47 tu\u1ed5i tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n vs Anh, v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0a Tam S\u01b0 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup sau 28 n\u0103m.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/thay-gi-sau-dem-lich-su-sang-trang-cho-nguoi-anh-tren-cham-11m-421-190321.html\" target=\"_blank\">Chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng k\u1ecbch t\u00ednh sang trang l\u1ecbch s\u1eed tr\u00ean ch\u1ea5m 11m</span> tr\u01b0\u1edbc Colombia c\u0169ng l\u00e0 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean Anh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u1edf n\u1ee5 c\u01b0\u1eddi sau 12 n\u0103m to\u00e0n nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1eafng cay \u1edf v\u00f2ng knock-out c\u00e1c gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1edbn. Tam S\u01b0 c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 m\u1ea5t t\u1eebng \u0111\u00f3 th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u01a1i tr\u1eadn t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup v\u00e0 gi\u1edd \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u m\u1ed9t Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 \u0111\u00e1ng s\u1ee3, h\u1ecd \u0111\u1ee9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u1ea3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup sau 28 n\u0103m.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Southgate ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u tr\u1eadn Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n vs Anh h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Southgate ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u tr\u1eadn Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n vs Anh h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/4/hlv-southgate-bay-gio-hoac-khong-bao-gio-cho-dt-anh.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>HLV Southgate ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u tr\u1eadn Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n vs Anh</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u00dd th\u1ee9c t\u1ea7m c\u1ee1 quan tr\u1ecdng, HLV Southgate ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u tr\u1eadn Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n vs Anh nh\u1eb1m hi\u1ec7u tri\u1ec7u tinh th\u1ea7n c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2: &ldquo;C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi ch\u00fang t\u00f4i, b\u00e2y gi\u1edd ho\u1eb7c kh\u00f4ng bao gi\u1edd. \u0110\u00e2y th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i l\u1edbn v\u00e0 m\u1eb7c d\u00f9 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd c\u00f2n tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh h\u01a1n n\u1eefa, t\u00f4i s\u1ee3 r\u1eb1ng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i n\u00e0o nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0o n\u1eefa trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai.&rdquo;<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">&ldquo;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i d\u00e0nh s\u1ef1 t\u00f4n tr\u1ecdng tuy\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ed1i cho Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n, trong khi t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 lu\u00f4n b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 th\u1ea5p trong qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9 m\u1eb7c d\u00f9 th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean g\u00e2y kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n cho ch\u00fang ta. Sai l\u1ea7m \u0111\u00f3 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e9p l\u1eb7p l\u1ea1i, nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 khi ch\u00ednh h\u1ecd m\u1edbi l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi gi\u00e0 d\u1eb7n, gi\u00e0u kinh nghi\u1ec7m v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea1t th\u00e0nh t\u00edch t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n ch\u00fang t\u00f4i.&rdquo;<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Southgate d\u00e8 ch\u1eebng Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n v\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i x\u00e3 giao g\u00ec, nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 khi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0 v\u00f2ng t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t k\u1ef3 World Cup ch\u1ee9a \u0111\u1ef1ng qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd. Th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf, \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n B\u1eafc \u00c2u lu\u00f4n l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 kh\u00f3 ch\u1ecbu cho Anh khi \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng thua trong hai l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 \u1edf c\u00e1c k\u1ef3 World Cup li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp 2002 v\u00e0 2006. \u0110\u1ed9i th\u1eafng trong c\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y s\u1ebd ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n Croatia ho\u1eb7c ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Nga \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u00e1n k\u1ebft.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/cuu-hlv-anh-bat-ngo-ung-ho-thuy-dien-chien-thang-421-190396.html\">C\u1ef1u HLV Anh b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/du-am-thuy-dien-vs-thuy-si-nguoi-hung-emil-forsberg-421-190326.html\">Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n-kh\u00f4ng-Ibra ti\u1ebfn xa \u1edf World Cup: H\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh phi th\u01b0\u1eddng vi\u1ebft b\u1edfi ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng b\u00ecnh th\u01b0\u1eddng</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong><o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"955","checkdouble":"190481"},{"date":"09:52 06/07","title":"B\u1ecb FIFA tu\u00fdt c\u00f2i v\u00ec l\u1ed9ng ng\u00f4n, Diego Maradona bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i xin l\u1ed7i","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/28/bi-fifa-tuyt-coi-vi-long-ngon-diego-maradona-xin-loi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>B\u1ecb FIFA c\u1ea3nh c\u00e1o, Diego Maradona xin l\u1ed7i v\u00ec nh\u1eefng ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u thi\u1ebfu suy ngh\u0129 v\u1ec1 tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i sau khi \u0110T Anh \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Colombia. </h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Diego Maradona xin l\u1ed7i<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">L\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea1i s\u1ee9 World Cup 2018 nh\u01b0ng Diego Maradona khi\u1ebfn FIFA ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u01b0a ra l\u1eddi c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o khi c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng ph\u00e1t ng\u00f4n kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00fang m\u1ef1c sau tr\u1eadn Anh vs Colombia t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 1/8. Maradona t\u1ecf th\u00e1i \u0111\u1ed9 gh\u00e9t \u0110T Anh ra m\u1eb7t, ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i Mark Geiger thi\u00ean v\u1ecb cho Tam S\u01b0.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"B\u1ecb FIFA tu\u00fdt c\u00f2i v\u00ec l\u1ed9ng ng\u00f4n, Diego Maradona xin l\u1ed7i h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"B\u1ecb FIFA tu\u00fdt c\u00f2i v\u00ec l\u1ed9ng ng\u00f4n, Diego Maradona xin l\u1ed7i h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/28/bi-fifa-tuyt-coi-vi-long-ngon-diego-maradona-xin-loi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Diego Maradona xin l\u1ed7i sau khi c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng ph\u00e1t ng\u00f4n kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00fang m\u1ef1c d\u00f9 l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea1i s\u1ee9 World Cup 2018.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nFIFA sau \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eedi l\u1eddi c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ebfn Maradona nh\u1eb1m nh\u1eafc nh\u1edf &quot;c\u1eadu b\u00e9 v\u00e0ng&quot; \u0111i\u1ec1u ch\u1ec9nh l\u1ea1i cho ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi c\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ecb \u0111ang nh\u1eadn.&nbsp;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u1ecb FIFA c\u1ea3nh c\u00e1o, Maradona m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y ph\u1ea3i g\u1eedi l\u1eddi xin l\u1ed7i tr\u00ean Instagram c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n: &quot;T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i \u0111i\u1ec1u v\u00e0, xin kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh, m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 l\u00e0 kh\u00f3 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn. Xin l\u1ed7i FIFA v\u00e0 ng\u00e0i ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch. \u0110\u00f4i khi t\u00f4i c\u00f3 \u00fd ki\u1ebfn tr\u00e1i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1edbi quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh, nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n t\u00f4n tr\u1ecdng c\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng c\u1ee7a ban t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c v\u00e0 tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i&quot;.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Maradona g\u00e2y tranh c\u00e3i<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u00ean c\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ecb l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea1i s\u1ee9 World Cup 2018, Maradona g\u00e2y ra r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u tranh c\u00e3i k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u gi\u1ea3i. \u00d4ng b\u1ecb b\u1eaft g\u1eb7p ph\u00ec ph\u00e8o h\u00fat x\u00ec g\u00e0 trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa Argentina vs Iceland, hay b\u1ecb t\u1ed1 gi\u01a1 ng\u00f3n tay th\u1ed1i trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa Argentina vs Nigeria.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau khi ra vi\u1ec7n, Maradona c\u0169ng g\u00e2y tranh c\u00e3i khi tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 trao gi\u1ea3i 8.000 b\u1ea3ng cho ai t\u00ecm ra tung t\u00edch k\u1ebb phao tin m\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ebft. Nh\u1eefng vi\u1ec7c l\u00e0m ph\u1ea3n c\u1ea3m, thi\u1ebfu suy ngh\u0129 c\u1ee7a Maradona khi\u1ebfn FIFA \u0111au \u0111\u1ea7u v\u00e0 bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng c\u1ea3nh c\u00e1o d\u00f9 gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u s\u1eafp k\u1ebft th\u00fac.<br>\r\n<h2>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn v\u1ec1 Diego Maradona t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018:</h2>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/fifa-ra-toi-hau-thu-cho-maradona-vi-thoi-long-ngon-421-190415.html\">FIFA ra t\u1ed1i h\u1eadu th\u01b0 cho Maradona v\u00ec th\u00f3i l\u1ed9ng ng\u00f4n</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/hau-truong/vua-bong-da-maradona-treo-thuong-8000-bang-truy-tim-ke-tung-tin-minh-chet-188-190165.html\">Vua b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Maradona treo th\u01b0\u1edfng 8.000 b\u1ea3ng truy t\u00ecm k\u1ebb tung tin m\u00ecnh ch\u1ebft</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/maradona-phat-bieu-ve-dt-argentina-bi-loai-421-190100.html\">Maradona: &ldquo;Argentina b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t b\u1ed9 phim ch\u1ebft ch\u00f3c&rdquo;</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/maradona-xuat-vien-toi-dang-cang-tran-suc-song-hon-bao-gio-het-421-189895.html\">Maradona xu\u1ea5t vi\u1ec7n: &ldquo;T\u00f4i \u0111ang c\u0103ng tr\u00e0n s\u1ee9c s\u1ed1ng h\u01a1n bao gi\u1edd h\u1ebft&rdquo;</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/maradona-phat-bieu-ve-iniesta-va-danh-loi-khen-421-190004.html\">Iniesta l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t qu\u00fd \u00f4ng, Ramos l\u00e0 k\u1ebb ph\u00e0m phu</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/maradona-bao-ve-messi-chi-trich-nhan-to-khac-cua-argentina-421-188795.html\">Maradona b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 Messi, c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 quan tr\u1ecdng kh\u00e1c c\u1ee7a Argentina</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<strong><br type=\"_moz\">\r\n</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>N.D (TTVN)&nbsp;</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"954","checkdouble":"190482"}]}